The burial rites of the late Sir Christopher Ajakpovi Oyegwa (KSC) began on Wednesday with a service of songs in Warri, Delta State. Commendation service holds tomorrow at St. Peter’s Anglican Church, Igbudu, Warri. Funeral service will hold at St. Mary’s Catholic Church, Okpawha-Aviara, Isoko, Delta State followed by reception in the community. Thanksgiving service is at Saint Peters Anglican Church, off Deco Road, Warri.